'''理查德·艾莱弗·艾欧阿德'''（{{lang-en|Richard Ellef Ayoade}}，{{IPAc-en|aɪ|.|ɔː|ˈ|ɑː|d|eɪ}}，{{bd|1977年|6月12日|}}）是一位[[英国|英国]][[喜剧演员|喜剧演员]]、电视[[節目主持人|節目主持人]]和[[导演|导演]]，他最知名的角色为英剧《[[IT狂人|IT狂人]]》中的莫里斯·莫斯（{{lang|en|Maurice Moss}}）。他的导演作品有电影《[[初戀潛水艇|初戀潛水艇]]》和《{{link-en|盜貼人生|The Double (2013 film)}}》，以及多个著名乐队的[[音乐影片|音乐影片]]，包括[[北极猴乐队|北极猴乐队]]、[[吸血鬼週末|吸血鬼週末]]、{{lang|en|[[Yeah_yeah_yeahs|Yeah yeah yeahs]]}}和[[卡薩比恩|卡薩比恩]]的{{lang|en|MV}}。

== 早年 ==
艾欧阿德出生于伦敦[[漢默史密斯|漢默史密斯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://search.findmypast.co.uk/results/world-records/england-and-wales-births-1837-2006?firstname=richard&lastname=ayoade|title=Richard Ayoade|publisher=Findmypast.co.uk|accessdate=4 January 2015|archive-date=2017-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020084200/https://search.findmypast.co.uk/results/world-records/england-and-wales-births-1837-2006?firstname=richard&lastname=ayoade|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父亲为[[尼日利亚|尼日利亚]]人拉伊德·阿德·拉蒂提·艾欧阿德（{{lang|en|Layide Ade Laditi Ayoade}}），母亲为[[挪威|挪威]]人达格尼·阿玛丽·巴苏伊克（{{lang|en|Dagny Amalie Baassuik}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.filmmagasinet.no/no/Intervjuer/Hoy-kred-og-halvt-norsk/|title=Høy kred og halvt norsk|work=Film Magasinet|accessdate=4 January 2015|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222193705/http://www.filmmagasinet.no/no/Intervjuer/Hoy-kred-og-halvt-norsk/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/theticket/2011/0311/1224291811420.html| title = Moss becomes boss| date = 11 March 2011| work = The Irish Times}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.twcpublicity.com/downloads/production/submarine_notes_final_(1).pdf| title = Submarine production notes| author = [[Miramax_Films|Miramax Films]]| accessdate = 4 January 2015| date = 19 April 2012| format = PDF| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223329/http://www.twcpublicity.com/downloads/production/submarine_notes_final_(1).pdf| archive-date = 2016-03-03| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://naijalife.freehostia.com/mag/?p=673| title = Richard Ayoade Starts Production on New Project 'The Double'| date = 18 May 2012| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160112171017/http://naijalife.freehostia.com/mag/?p=673| archivedate = 2016年1月12日}}</ref>。他的姓氏在[[约鲁巴语|约鲁巴语]]中有“受祝福的王冠”或“王冠之喜”的意思<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.onlinenigeria.com/nigeriannames/ad.asp?blurb=820|title= Nigerian Names and Meanings: AYOADE|website= Online Nigeria|accessdate= 24 April 2014|archive-date= 2018-12-15|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181215173123/https://www.onlinenigeria.com/nigeriannames/ad.asp?blurb=820|dead-url= no}}</ref>。他小时候随家人搬到[[伊普斯威奇|伊普斯威奇]]居住<ref name="barkham">{{cite news| title = I really don't think I'm cool| author = Patrick Barkham| newspaper = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]| date = 1 October 2008| url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2008/oct/02/comedy.television| accessdate = 19 October 2012| archive-date = 2013-03-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130320032247/http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2008/oct/02/comedy.television| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

艾欧阿德在伊普斯威奇的圣约翰学院完成中学教育，随后进入[[剑桥大学圣凯瑟琳学院|剑桥大学圣凯瑟琳学院]]学习法律（1995–1998）<ref>{{cite web|first=Pat|last=Mills|url=http://patmills.wordpress.com/tag/st-josephs-college/|title=DREDD: HE IS THE LAW!|date=5 October 2012|publisher=wordpress.com|accessdate=5 April 2014|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301184420/https://patmills.wordpress.com/tag/st-josephs-college/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在1997年至1998年间担任大学戏剧社团[[脚灯社|脚灯社]]主席<ref>{{cite news| title = Why do posh comics who went to Oxford and Cambridge| url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2533157/Comedians-went-Oxbridge-Footlights-theatre-snapping-best-gigs-complains-Bob-Mortimer.html| accessdate = 2015-04-15| archive-date = 2021-03-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210301184353/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2533157/Comedians-went-Oxbridge-Footlights-theatre-snapping-best-gigs-complains-Bob-Mortimer.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>，并因戏剧制作获得马丁·史蒂勒奖（{{lang|en|Martin Steele Prize}}）<ref>{{cite web| url = https://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/reporter/1997-98/weekly/5747/23.html| title = Reporter 5/8/98: St Catharine's College| date = 5 August 1998| publisher = Cambridge University Reporter| access-date = 2015-04-15| archive-date = 2020-09-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200903041154/https://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/reporter/1997-98/weekly/5747/23.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 职业生涯 ==
在剑桥就读期间，艾欧阿德创作并参演了许多演出。他和当年的脚灯社副主席[[约翰·奥利弗|约翰·奥利弗]]一起创作了两部哑剧：《睡美人》和《格林童话》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theitcrowd.co.uk/cv/richard-ayoade.htm|title=Richard Ayoade – CV|publisher=theitcrowd.co.uk|accessdate=8 May 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140707130631/http://www.theitcrowd.co.uk/cv/richard-ayoade.htm|archivedate=2014年7月7日}}</ref>
。他与同样在脚灯社相识的同学{{link-en|马修·霍内斯|Matthew Holness}}合作撰写并参演了舞台剧《加斯·马伦基的惊吓骑士》（{{lang|en|''Garth Marenghi's Fright Knight''}}）。该剧在2000年的[[爱丁堡边缘艺术节|爱丁堡边缘艺术节]]上演出，并获得了[[皮埃尔喜剧奖|皮埃尔喜剧奖]]提名<ref name="Petridis">{{cite news |title=Richard Ayoade: Meet Mr Modest |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/jan/15/richard-ayoade-interview |author=Alexis Petridis |work=The Guardian |date=14 January 2011 |accessdate=4 January 2015 |archive-date=2013-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130716063904/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2011/jan/15/richard-ayoade-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2001年的爱丁堡边缘艺术节上，该剧的续篇《加斯·马伦基的地下脑袋》（{{lang|en|''Garth Marenghi's Netherhead''}}）为艾欧阿德赢得了皮埃尔喜剧奖<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Jo Unwin Literacy Agency |title=Richard Ayoade |url=http://www.jounwin.co.uk/richard-ayoade/ |accessdate=February 2014 |archive-date=2016-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729195016/http://www.jounwin.co.uk/richard-ayoade/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年，艾欧阿德和霍内斯把剧中角色加斯·马伦基搬上荧屏，创造了[[戏仿|戏仿]]电视剧《{{link-en|加斯·马伦基的黑暗地点|Garth Marenghi's Darkplace}}》，在英国[[第四台_(英國)|第四台]]播出。艾欧阿德和霍内斯两人在剧中分别扮演他们原来的角色。

2006年，艾欧阿德开始在第四台的情景喜剧《[[IT狂人|IT狂人]]》中扮演莫斯一角，在2008年获得了{{link-en|蒙特卡罗电视节|Monte-Carlo Television Festival}}的电视喜剧类杰出男演员奖。2014年，他因该剧的2013年特别篇获得了一项[[英国学术电视奖|英国学术电视奖]]喜剧节目类最佳表演奖<ref>{{cite web |first=Jess |last=Denham |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/tv-baftas-2014-winners-list-in-full-from-broadchurch-to-southcliffe-9392993.html |title=TV Baftas 2014: Winners' list in full from Broadchurch to Southcliffe |work=The Independent |date=18 May 2014 |accessdate=22 June 2014 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903041217/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/tv-baftas-2014-winners-list-in-full-from-broadchurch-to-southcliffe-9392993.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/i684851-9/bafta-television-awards-2014-bafta-television-awards-2014-richard-ayoade.html#~oPc7r1NZMDhSzS|website=Digitalspy|title=BAFTA Television awards 2014: Richard Ayoade with the BAFTA for Male Performance in a Comedy Programme|accessdate=7 September 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140907234421/http://m.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/i684851-9/bafta-television-awards-2014-bafta-television-awards-2014-richard-ayoade.html#~oPc7r1NZMDhSzS|archivedate=2014-09-07|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

2010年，艾欧阿德的导演处女作《[[初戀潛水艇|初戀潛水艇]]》在[[多伦多国际电影节|多伦多国际电影节]]上首映<ref>{{cite news |author=Brad Frenette |title=Toronto International Film Fest announces 2010 lineup |work=[[National_Post|National Post]] |date=27 July 2010 |url=http://arts.nationalpost.com/2010/07/27/happening-now-toronto-international-film-fest-announces-2010-galas/ |accessdate=19 October 2012 |archive-date=2012-07-08 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120708070736/http://arts.nationalpost.com/2010/07/27/happening-now-toronto-international-film-fest-announces-2010-galas/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该片是一部成长题材的喜剧，改编自2008年出版的同名小说。[[北极猴乐队|北极猴乐队]]主唱[[亚历克斯·特纳|亚历克斯·特纳]]为本片原声带创作了5首新歌。艾欧阿德凭此片获得了[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳新人奖提名。他还执导了2013年的[[黑色喜劇|黑色喜劇]]电影《{{link-en|盜貼人生|The Double (2013 film)}}》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/on-the-double-richard-ayoade-meets-his-match-20140509|website=Rolling Stone|title=On 'The Double':Richard Ayoade meets His Match|author=Sam Adams|date=9 May 2014|accessdate=7 September 2014|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818132101/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/on-the-double-richard-ayoade-meets-his-match-20140509|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该片由[[傑西·艾森柏格|傑西·艾森柏格]]和[[蜜雅·娃丝柯思卡|蜜雅·娃丝柯思卡]]主演<ref>{{cite news| url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jesse-eisenberg-mia-wasikowska-the-double-286385| title = Jesse Eisenberg, Mia Wasikowska Join 'The Double' Cast| first = Stuart| last = Kemp| work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]| date = 1 February 2012| accessdate = 19 October 2012| archive-date = 2013-11-05| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105043118/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jesse-eisenberg-mia-wasikowska-the-double-286385| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 私生活 ==
2007年，艾欧阿德与演员莉迪亚·福克斯（{{lang|en|Lydia Fox}}）结婚<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1799714/bio|title= Lydia Fox Bio|publisher= IMDb.com|accessdate= 2015-04-15|archive-date= 2021-03-01|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210301184428/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1799714/bio|dead-url= no}}</ref>。她是演艺世家{{link-en|罗宾·福克斯家族|Robin Fox family}}的一员，父亲为[[詹姆斯·福克斯|詹姆斯·福克斯]]，哥哥为[[劳伦斯·福克斯|劳伦斯·福克斯]]，嫂子为[[比莉·派佩|比莉·派佩]]。这对夫妇有两个孩子。

